channel.description: I've decided I'm going to take mine off, And start off with a brand new source and code it and stuff, so how do you delete your server?

item.title: How do you delete your server from the server status list?
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

Let the uptime decrease by turning your server off and it will eventually be kicked off the server status list. Locked because there really isn’t any further discussion needed on the topic.
